org.lappsgrid.discriminator

Interface Discriminator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DiscriminatorImpl

    public interface Discriminator
    Discriminator objects are used to provide type information about Data objects passed between LAPPS services.

    Discriminators support multiple inheritance and a Discriminator may have one or more parents.

    Author:
    Keith Suderman
